model

Class Inventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Inventory

  • public class Inventory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the Observable lists and various methods to update Parts/ Products and Lookup by ID/Name. A feature I would implement that would extend functionality is the capability to track orders and sales. This will allow the user to track which parts sell well with a product and which products overall are selling.
